      "review_summary": "This PR hardens release validation and publish/closeout automation by pinning workflow actions to SHAs, adding stable-main closeout, enforcing stable soak/performance evidence, adding Sigstore npm provenance verification, and updating release docs/tests.\n\nPR surface: Source 0, Tests +355, Docs +43, Config +380, Other +834. Total +1612 across 72 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source inspection is enough: the new workflow trusts the evidence JSON without verifying its checksum companion, and the new verifier enumerates only macOS release assets.",
